Title: The Drug Olympics
Plot: Recent losses inspire the team to hold a special lock-in at the Goat House as part of a team building exercise, but the night takes a bizarre turn when Alex and Thad split the players up into groups for a risky competition involving drugs.
ParentalRatingReason: Sex scenes, drug use & content that may offend
GuestStars: James Cade, Meghan Heffern, Omari Newton, Chantal Quesnelle, Rob Ramsay, Kwasi Songui
